519
00:25:44,500 --> 00:25:45,210
Daddy!

520
00:25:57,880 --> 00:26:00,460
This is not a small amount of money,

521
00:26:00,460 --> 00:26:01,970
Gu Nian. When we divorced,

522
00:26:01,970 --> 00:26:02,490
didn't we already

523
00:26:02,490 --> 00:26:03,770
divide the assets clearly?

524
00:26:03,850 --> 00:26:04,890
Now, my money,

525
00:26:05,050 --> 00:26:07,090
my money isn't just my own anymore!

526
00:26:07,090 --> 00:26:08,060
Do you understand?

527
00:26:08,080 --> 00:26:09,780
This isn't as simple as you think!

528
00:26:10,010 --> 00:26:11,610
I just want to get my money back.

529
00:26:11,940 --> 00:26:13,460
I want to give Doudou a chance to survive.

530
00:26:13,690 --> 00:26:14,810
Listen here, Gu Nian!

531
00:26:15,470 --> 00:26:17,180
I don't have the extra resources now

532
00:26:17,180 --> 00:26:18,920
