533
00:26:24,570 --> 00:26:25,290
Lyu Tu.

534
00:26:27,610 --> 00:26:29,360
You must have done a lot of bad things

535
00:26:30,000 --> 00:26:31,010
and are afraid of karma, aren't you?

536
00:26:31,250 --> 00:26:33,300
Gu Nian, she's pregnant.

537
00:26:33,330 --> 00:26:34,300
Don't go too far.

538
00:26:34,620 --> 00:26:35,690
When I was pregnant,

539
00:26:35,690 --> 00:26:36,930
you two were already together, weren't you?

540
00:26:37,130 --> 00:26:38,170
It's only been a few months since the divorce,

541
00:26:39,470 --> 00:26:40,660
and the child is already on the way.

542
00:26:41,210 --> 00:26:42,170
How this child came to be,

543
00:26:42,170 --> 00:26:43,290
you two know best!

544
00:26:44,610 --> 00:26:46,090
We were best friends.

545
00:26:47,810 --> 00:26:49,370
Yet you became the third party in my marriage!

546
00:26:49,390 --> 00:26:50,040
What are you doing?

547
00:26:50,110 --> 00:26:51,190
Don't touch her!

548
00:26:54,010 --> 00:26:54,530
Gu Nian.

549
00:26:55,410 --> 00:26:57,970
You take my hard-earned savings,

550
00:26:58,250 --> 00:26:59,610
and you still talk to me like this,

551
00:26:59,610 --> 00:27:01,010
being all aggressive, huh?

552
00:27:01,550 --> 00:27:02,430
Let me tell you,

553
00:27:02,770 --> 00:27:05,250
when I was with Feng Huanan,

554
00:27:05,250 --> 00:27:07,010
you weren't even in the picture.

555
00:27:07,480 --> 00:27:09,040
You have no part in this!

556
00:27:09,600 --> 00:27:10,510
You call me the third party?

557
00:27:11,340 --> 00:27:12,760
You're the real intruder!

558
00:27:12,790 --> 00:27:13,470
You know that?

559
00:27:31,600 --> 00:27:32,340
Mr. Zhang,

